01:07.024 --> 01:09.654
[alarm rings]

01:11.407 --> 01:13.035
Did you hit snooze or off?

01:13.036 --> 01:15.749
- Off.
- Really?

01:15.750 --> 01:17.460
Maybe I hit snooze.

01:17.461 --> 01:20.466
Can we talk about setting
realistic alarm goals?

01:20.467 --> 01:21.886
Huh?

01:21.887 --> 01:24.516
Like, if you wanna get up at 7:30,

01:24.517 --> 01:27.731
could you maybe not
set the alarm for 6:45?

01:27.732 --> 01:30.069
Yeah, but I like
to ease into my morning.

01:30.070 --> 01:32.824
But I wake up and then
I can't get back to sleep

01:32.825 --> 01:36.373
and then I move, and then you wake up,

01:36.374 --> 01:38.126
and you think it's intentional,

01:38.127 --> 01:41.791
and then my first feeling
of the day is guilt.

01:42.135 --> 01:45.265
Also, can we
spend the night at my place,

01:45.266 --> 01:47.228
like, once in a while?

01:47.229 --> 01:49.942
'Cause Malibu is so far away.

01:49.943 --> 01:52.113
Of course. I'm so sorry, okay?

01:52.114 --> 01:53.783
I didn't know about the alarm thing.

01:53.784 --> 01:55.327
- Mm.
- All you had to do was ask.

01:55.328 --> 01:57.289
Thank you.

01:57.290 --> 01:59.753
All right, well, I'm up.

01:59.754 --> 02:02.425
Let there be light. Ova, turn up.

02:02.426 --> 02:04.345
OVA: Good morning, John.

02:04.346 --> 02:07.894
[blinds whirring]

02:07.895 --> 02:09.898
[smooching]

